data.description: Two master bedrooms, one downstairs and one upstairs.  A total of five bedrooms with four upstairs and one master down.  Foyer and formal dining room has engineered hardwood flooring.  Kitchen has granite counter tops, an island and all appliances in kitchen to remain including refrigerator.  Kitchen is open to the greatroom.  There is 1/2 bath for guests downstairs.  The home has washer and dryer connections downstairs and also upstairs.  The master downstairs has a walkin closet a private bath with granite vanity with dual sinks, a large soaker tub and a walkin shower.  Upstairs has a large greatroom, a full hall bath, four bedrooms one being a second master with a large private bath with dual sinks and a private balcony.  Two car garage, a back patio and a great place to call home.
